summary: An ordinance relating to the vacation of West 110 feet of Alley, Block 6, Edgewater Addition, being the alley between Lots 11 and 13 Inclusive, and Lot 14, said Block from Interlake Avenue to a line 110 feet East of and parallel therewith, and authorizing the City Engineer to sign a petition therefor, being City Comptroller's File No. 193058.
